# Diaspore default apps (DIA-20260617-06) — pinned F-Droid versions.
#
# These APKs are NOT committed (~277 MB; Fennec alone is 120 MB). fetch-default-apps.sh downloads them
# from F-Droid into this dir before a build; the Android.bp android_app_import modules then bake them into
# /product/app (presigned: F-Droid's own signature is kept, so F-Droid can update them in place later).
# Run `bash fetch-default-apps.sh` once on a fresh tree before `m systemimage`. (FDroid.apk predates this
# and stays committed.)
